    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1516150/extras/d7b80e15f33c424fa4e77c4aa1f8cf6a.avif?t=1753171302\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Dorpie, where the sky's the limit – literally! This casual city builder challenges you to construct a whimsical vertical town that defies gravity and ignites your imagination. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Dorpie?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dorpie <i>(pronounced &quot;DOR-pee&quot;)</i> is an Afrikaans word meaning &quot;small town.&quot; But there's nothing small about the vertically sprawling villages you'll create! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1516150/extras/0e42ce21ea011bbba837c8bfac7d67c3.poster.avif?t=1753171302\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1516150/extras/0e42ce21ea011bbba837c8bfac7d67c3.webm?t=1753171302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1516150/extras/0e42ce21ea011bbba837c8bfac7d67c3.mp4?t=1753171302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with a limited plot of land and a handful of structures. As you build and complete objectives, you'll unlock new buildings, decorations, and platforms. With horizontal space at a premium, your only option is to build up, up, up! Rotate and stack structures to create a unique skyline that showcases your creativity and problem-solving skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1516150/extras/704d491a13e51a9fd148c3a54e883ac2.avif?t=1753171302\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vertical Stacking: Master the art of building upwards to create towering masterpieces. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Objective-Based Progression: Complete goals to unlock new content and expand your possibilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing Gameplay: Enjoy a stress-free building experience with no time pressure. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibrant Visuals: Immerse yourself in colorful, charming environments full of personality. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Creativity: Discover new visual themes and structures with each play session. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Sets Dorpie Apart</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Vertical Focus: Unlike traditional city builders, Dorpie challenges you to think vertically. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for Short Sessions: Ideal for players who want to create something amazing in bite-sized chunks. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Complex Management: Focus on creativity without worrying about intricate resource systems. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What Dorpie Does Not Offer</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complex resource management </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat or violence </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin each run with an empty play area and a limited number of build tokens. As you construct your Dorpie, you'll uncover objectives. Complete them to earn more tokens and unlock new goals, gradually building your way to a legendary vertical village! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dorpie is lovingly crafted by Jeremy, a solo game developer from South Africa passionate about creating relaxing and creative experiences. Your feedback and suggestions are always welcome!</p>",
